Immediate past governor of Ekiti state, Ayodele Fayose is receiving medical attention after he was involved in an auto accident in Lagos, according to his media aide, Lere Olayinka. Olayinka disclosed this on his verifed Twitter handle. He said, “Immediate past Governor of Ekiti State, Mr Ayodele Fayose was involved in auto accident on 3rd Mainland Bridge in Lagos few minutes ago. He is in stable condition as I write while he is receiving medical attention” Immediate past Governor of Ekiti State, Mr Ayodele Fayose was involved in auto accident on 3rd Mainland Bridge in Lagos few minutes ago. He is in stable condition as I write while he is receiving medical attention. — Lere Olayinka – Aresa 1 (@OlayinkaLere) December 5, 2018 